General.Name: Arogo Capital Acquisition Corp Unit
General.Description: Arogo Capital Acquisition Corp. does not have significant operations. The company focuses on effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or related business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to focus on businesses in transportation and technology industries within the electric vehicles technology, smart mobility, or sustainable transportation. Arogo Capital Acquisition Corp. was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Miami, Florida.
